account_sid.description: The unique identifier of the account that owns this queue.

average_wait_time.description: The average time, in seconds, that callers have spent waiting in this queue.

current_size.description: The current number of callers waiting in this queue.

date_created.description: The date and time when this queue was created.

date_updated.description: The date and time when this queue was last updated.

friendly_name.description: A user-defined human-readable name for this queue.

max_size.description: The maximum number of callers allowed in this queue.

sid.description: A unique identifier for this queue.

uri.description: The URI for this queue resource.

subresource_uris.description: Contains URIs for related subresources of this queue.

members.description: A URI to fetch the members (callers) of this queue.
